object.script:
function onTick() output.setBool(2, auto) output.setBool(3, alti) output.setBool(4, front) output.setBool(5, flood)
inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1)
pitch = input.getNumber(5) roll = input.getNumber(6) yaw = input.getNumber(7) ud = input.getNumber(8) alarm = input.getBool(4)
autofeed = input.getBool(2) altifeed = input.getBool(3) frontfeed = input.getBool(5) floodfeed = input.getBool(6)
propoff = input.getBool(6) land = input.getBool(7) vtoloff = input.getBool(8) sub = input.getBool(9) subactive = input.getBool(10)
badPilot = input.getBool(5)
auto = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 2, 80, 70, 13) --auto alti = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 2, 65, 93, 13) --alti front = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 100, 2, 55, 30) flood = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 100, 35, 55, 30)
end
function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(250, 150, 0) screen.drawRect(5, 5, 10, 30) --pitch screen.drawRect(20, 5, 10, 30) --ud screen.drawRect(60, 5, 30, 10) --roll screen.drawRect(60, 20, 30, 10) --yaw
screen.setColor(0,150,250) screen.drawRectF(5, 20, 10, (pitch*-15)) --pitch screen.drawRectF(20, 20, 10, (ud*-15)) --ud screen.drawRectF(75, 5, (roll*15), 10) --roll screen.drawRectF(75, 20, (yaw*15), 10) --yaw screen.drawText(8, 37, "p") screen.drawText(23, 37, "c") screen.drawText(38, 8, "roll") screen.drawText(38, 23, "yaw")
screen.setColor(0,150,250) --button boxes screen.drawRect(2, 80, 50, 13) --auto screen.drawRect(2, 80, 70, 13) screen.drawRect(2, 65, 73, 13) --alti screen.drawRect(2, 65, 93, 13)
screen.setColor(0,150,250) screen.drawText(5, 84, "autopilot") screen.drawText(5, 69, "altitude hold")
if autofeed then screen.setColor(0, 250, 0) screen.drawText(57, 84, "on") screen.setColor(100, 100, 100, 100) screen.drawRectF(2, 80, 70, 13) else screen.setColor(250, 0, 0) screen.drawText(57, 84, "off") screen.setColor(50, 50, 50, 100) screen.drawRectF(2, 80, 70, 13) end
if altifeed then screen.setColor(0, 250, 0) screen.drawText(80, 69, "on") screen.setColor(100, 100, 100, 100) screen.drawRectF(2, 65, 93, 13) else screen.setColor(250, 0, 0) screen.drawText(80, 69, "off") screen.setColor(50, 50, 50, 100) screen.drawRectF(2, 65, 93, 13) end
if alarm then screen.setColor(250, 0, 0) screen.drawText(5,55,"Alarm!") else screen.setColor(0, 250, 0) screen.drawText(5,55,"all systems good") end
screen.setColor(250, 150, 0) screen.drawRect(100, 2, 55, 20) screen.drawRect(100, 2, 55, 30)
screen.drawTextBox(105, 7,45,10, "front lights",0,0)
if frontfeed then screen.setColor(0, 250, 0) screen.drawTextBox(105, 24,45,8, "on",0,0) screen.setColor(100, 100, 100, 100) screen.drawRectF(100, 2, 55, 30) else screen.setColor(250, 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(105, 24,45,8 ,"off",0,0) screen.setColor(50, 50, 50, 100) screen.drawRectF(100, 2, 55, 30) end
screen.setColor(250, 150, 0) screen.drawRect(100, 35, 55, 20) screen.drawRect(100, 35, 55, 30)
screen.drawTextBox(105, 40,45,10, "flood lights",0,0)
if floodfeed then screen.setColor(0, 250, 0) screen.drawTextBox(105, 57,45,8, "on",0,0) screen.setColor(100, 100, 100, 100) screen.drawRectF(100, 35, 55, 30) else screen.setColor(250, 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(105, 57,45,8 ,"off",0,0) screen.setColor(50, 50, 50, 100) screen.drawRectF(100,35, 55, 30) end
end

object.script:
zoom = 1 yb=0 xb=0 h=0 function onTick()
ButtonPlus = {x=3,y=h-31,r=8} ButtonMinus = {x=3,y=h-22,r=8} ButtonUp = {x=12,y=h-20,r=9} ButtonDown = {x=12,y=h-11,r=9} ButtonLeft = {x=3,y=h-11,r=9} ButtonRight = {x=21,y=h-11,r=9} ButtonReset = {x=3,y=h-43,r=9}
TouchX = input.getNumber(3) TouchY = input.getNumber(4) Touchinput = input.getBool(1) x = input.getNumber(7) y = input.getNumber(8) autox = input.getNumber(9) autoy = input.getNumber(10) autopilot = input.getBool(7)
if Touchinput == true then if TouchX >= ButtonPlus.x and TouchX <= ButtonPlus.x+ButtonPlus.r then if TouchY >= ButtonPlus.y and TouchY <= ButtonPlus.y+ButtonPlus.r then zoom = zoom-0.05 elseif TouchY >= ButtonMinus.y and TouchY <= ButtonMinus.y+ButtonMinus.r then zoom = zoom+0.05 end end
if TouchX >= ButtonUp.x and TouchX <= ButtonUp.x+ButtonUp.r then --x position check if TouchY >= ButtonUp.y and TouchY <= ButtonUp.y+ButtonUp.r then --y position check yb = yb+(10*zoom) --changes value when all checks are true end end
if TouchX >= ButtonDown.x and TouchX <= ButtonDown.x+ButtonDown.r then if TouchY >= ButtonDown.y and TouchY <= ButtonDown.y+ButtonDown.r then yb = yb-(10*zoom) end end
if TouchX >= ButtonLeft.x and TouchX <= ButtonLeft.x+ButtonLeft.r then if TouchY >= ButtonLeft.y and TouchY <= ButtonLeft.y+ButtonLeft.r then xb = xb-(10*zoom) end end
if TouchX >= ButtonRight.x and TouchX <= ButtonRight.x+ButtonRight.r then if TouchY >= ButtonRight.y and TouchY <= ButtonRight.y+ButtonRight.r then xb = xb+(10*zoom) end end
if TouchX >= ButtonReset.x and TouchX <= ButtonReset.x+ButtonReset.r then if TouchY >= ButtonReset.y and TouchY <= ButtonReset.y+ButtonReset.r then xb = 0 yb = 0 end end
end --clamp of zoom value if zoom < 0.1 then zoom = 0.1 end if zoom > 50 then zoom = 50 end end

function onTick() tilt = input.getNumber(1)*360 -- Tilt (Forward tilt sensor) supplied through composite 1 maxAngle = 90-math.abs(tilt) rollAngle = (input.getNumber(2)*360)/maxAngle*90 -- Roll (Right tilt sensor) supplied through composite 2 vertCheck = input.getNumber(3)>=0 if not vertCheck then -- Vertical check (Up tilt sensor) supplied through composite 3 tilt = tilt*-1 rollAngle = rollAngle*-1 end
armed = input.getBool(1) rockets = input.getNumber(4) missiles = input.getNumber(5)
end
function calcXY(x,y,bearing,distance) bearing = math.rad(bearing + 90) y = y+math.cos(bearing) * -distance x = x+math.sin(bearing) * distance return x,y end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
if vertCheck then screen.setColor(100, 50, 0) else screen.setColor(0,50,255) end for lineAngle = -90, 90, lineDist do if lineAngle>0 and vertCheck then screen.setColor(50,50,255) elseif lineAngle>0 and not vertCheck then screen.setColor(100,50,0) end lineLen = (maxLineWidth*w)*(1-math.abs(lineAngle)/lineDivideFactor) currentY = (tilt-lineAngle)*pixPerDegree*yMod mX, mY = calcXY(w/2,h/2,rollAngle+90,currentY) lX, lY = calcXY(mX,mY,rollAngle,lineLen/2) rX, rY = calcXY(mX,mY,rollAngle+180,lineLen/2) screen.drawLine(lX,lY,rX,rY) end centerY = h/2+tilt*pixPerDegree*yMod screen.setColor(125,125,125) mX, mY = calcXY(w/2,h/2,rollAngle+90,tilt*pixPerDegree*yMod) lX, lY = calcXY(mX,mY,rollAngle,100) rX, rY = calcXY(mX,mY,rollAngle+180,100) screen.drawLine(lX,lY,rX,rY) screen.setColor(255,0,0) screen.drawRectF(w/2-1,h/2,2,2)
if armed then screen.drawText(5,10,"rockets left:") screen.drawText(5,20,string.format("%.0f", rockets))
screen.drawText(5,35,"missiles left:") screen.drawText(5,45,string.format("%.0f", missiles)) end end

function onTick() speed = input.getNumber(1) rrps = input.getNumber(2) fuel = input.getNumber(3) fuelcap = input.getNumber(4) fuelcurr = input.getNumber(5) battery = input.getNumber(6) rudder = input.getNumber(7) altitude = input.getNumber(8) stabile = input.getNumber(9) alarm = input.getBool(1) gear = input.getBool(2) gen2 = input.getBool(3) rps = input.getNumber(10) range = input.getNumber(11) eta = input.getNumber(12) etamin = input.getNumber(13) dest = input.getBool(4) stable = input.getBool(5)
end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(250, 160, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 200, 3) screen.drawRectF(0, 15, 200, 3) screen.drawRectF(0, 40, 200, 3) screen.drawRectF(40, 40, 3, 100) screen.drawRectF(100, 0, 3, 40) screen.drawRectF(129, 40, 3, 100)
screen.setColor(250, 160, 0)
screen.drawText(2, 22, "vtol rps:") screen.drawText(45, 47, "Fuel remaining:") screen.drawText(75, 55, "/") screen.drawText(2, 47, "Fuel:") screen.drawText(5, 7, "knots:") screen.drawText(2, 29, "boosters Rps:") screen.drawText(45, 62, "kilometers range:") screen.drawText(2, 62, "battery:") screen.drawText(107, 22, "altitude:") --screen.drawText(2, 76, "engine-") --screen.drawText(2, 82, "battery:") screen.drawText(135, 45, "eta:") screen.drawText(135, 59, "hours") screen.drawText(135, 75, "mins")
screen.setColor(250, 250, 0) --screen.drawText(45, 81, "Generator 1:") --screen.drawText(45, 88, "Generator 2:")
screen.setColor(0, 150, 250)
screen.drawText(65, 22, string.format("%.2f", rps)) screen.drawText(35, 7, string.format("%.2f", speed)) screen.drawText(65, 29, string.format("%.2f", rrps)) screen.drawText(2, 55, string.format("%.1f", fuel)) screen.drawText(24, 55, "%") screen.drawText(45, 55, string.format("%.0f", fuelcurr)) screen.drawText(80, 55, string.format("%.0f", fuelcap)) screen.drawText(45, 69, string.format("%.0f", range)) screen.drawText(2, 69, string.format("%.1f", battery)) screen.drawText(24, 69, "%") screen.drawText(107, 29, string.format("%.1f", altitude)) --screen.drawText(2, 88, string.format("%.1f", engbattery)) --screen.drawText(24, 88, "%") screen.drawText(135, 53, string.format("%.0f", eta)) screen.drawText(135, 67, string.format("%.0f", etamin))
if gear then screen.setColor(0, 250, 0) screen.drawText(45, 77, "Landing Gear Up") else screen.setColor(250,0,0) screen.drawText(45, 77, "Landing Gear Down") end
if stable then screen.setColor(0, 250, 0) screen.drawText(45, 86, "engines stable") else screen.setColor(250,0,0) screen.drawText(45, 86, "adjusting engines") end
if dest then screen.setColor(250, 0, 0) screen.drawRect(10, 78, 70, 15) screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawRectF(11, 79, 69, 14) screen.setColor(0, 250, 0) screen.drawTextBox(10, 78, 70, 15, "destination reached",0,0) end
end
